description:
AnrFunction: Table containing configuration parameters for ANR (Avoid Neighboring Radio) function in a 5G network.

dateTime: Timestamp of the recorded configuration.
Area_Name: Geographic area where the configuration applies (e.g., cell site location).
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  Likely an arbitrary identifier; purpose unclear from sample data.
vsDataType: Type of data, specifying it relates to ANR function configuration.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
AnrFunction.removeGnbTime: Time threshold for removing gNB entries from ANR list.
AnrFunction.removeEnbTime: Time threshold for removing eNB entries from ANR list.
AnrFunction.anrFunctionId: Identifier of the specific ANR function instance.
AnrFunction.removeFreqRelTime: Time threshold for removing frequency-related entries.
AnrFunction.removeNrelTime: Time threshold for removing NR-related entries.
AnrFunction.pciConflictMobilityEcgiMeas: Flag indicating if PCI conflict measurement is enabled for mobility.
AnrFunction.plmnWhiteListUtranEnabled: Flag for enabling UTRAN PLMN whitelist.
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary13: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.probCellDetectLowHoSuccTime: Time threshold for low handover success probability cell detection.
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary12: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary7: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary11: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary10: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary9: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.removeNcellTime: Time threshold for removing neighboring cell entries.
AnrFunction.perCgiMeasPlmnWhiteListUtran: Flag indicating per CGI measurement for UTRAN PLMN whitelist.
AnrFunction.prioHoSuccRate: Priority handover success rate threshold.
AnrFunction.perCgiMeasPlmnWhiteListGeran: Flag indicating per CGI measurement for GERAN PLMN whitelist.
AnrFunction.maxTimeEventBasedPciConf: Maximum time for event-based PCI conflict.
AnrFunction.cellRelHoAttRateThreshold: Cell release handover attempt rate threshold.
AnrFunction.pciConflictDetectionEcgiMeas: Flag indicating if PCI conflict detection measurement is enabled.
AnrFunction.probCellDetectMedHoSuccThres: Threshold for medium handover success probability cell detection.
AnrFunction.removeNgnbTime: Time threshold for removing gNB entries from ANR list (potentially different from removeGnbTime).
AnrFunction.prioHoRate: Priority handover rate threshold.
AnrFunction.perEcgiMeasPlmnWhiteList: Flag indicating per ECGI measurement for PLMN whitelist.
AnrFunction.plmnWhiteListEnabled: Flag for enabling PLMN whitelist.
AnrFunction.probCellDetectLowHoSuccThres: Threshold for low handover success probability cell detection.
AnrFunction.s1HoPrepConsFailThres: S1 handover preparation consistency failure threshold.
AnrFunction.detectObsoleteExtCellsEnabled: Flag for enabling detection of obsolete external cells.
AnrFunction.prioTime: Priority time threshold.
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary1: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.removeNenbTime: Time threshold for removing eNB entries from ANR list (potentially different from removeEnbTime).
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary2: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary3: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary4: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary5: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.zzzTemporary6: Placeholder for future use.
AnrFunction.plmnWhiteListGeranEnabled: Flag for enabling GERAN PLMN whitelist.
AnrFunction.problematicCellPolicy: Policy for handling problematic cells.
AnrFunction.probCellDetectMedHoSuccTime: Time threshold for medium handover success probability cell detection.
AnrFunction.maxNoPciReportsEvent: Maximum number of PCI reports for an event.
